{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"96869c99-e033-4954-a784-caec4c977c90","content":"No existing files found — this is a guidance question. Here's how to convert your page:\n\n### 1. Add `x:DataType` to your XAML\n\nIn `SettingsPage.xaml`, add the `x:DataType` attribute to the root `ContentPage` element, pointing to your ViewModel's CLR type:\n\n```xml\n<ContentPage xmlns=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/dotnet/2021/maui\"\n             xmlns:x=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2009/xaml\"\n             xmlns:vm=\"clr-namespace:YourApp.ViewModels\"\n             x:DataType=\"vm:SettingsViewModel\"\n             x:Class=\"YourApp.Views.SettingsPage\">\n    <VerticalStackLayout Padding=\"20\" Spacing=\"15\">\n\n        <Label Text=\"{Binding Theme}\" />\n\n        <Switch IsToggled=\"{Binding NotificationsEnabled}\" />\n\n        <Label Text=\"{Binding FontSize, StringFormat='Font size: {0}'}\" />\n\n    </VerticalStackLayout>\n</ContentPage>\n```\n\nThe key change is:\n- **`xmlns:vm`** — imports the namespace containing your ViewModel.\n- **`x:DataType=\"vm:SettingsViewModel\"`** — enables compiled bindings for the entire page.\n\n### 2. Catch binding errors at build time\n\nAdd this to your `.csproj`:\n\n```xml\n<PropertyGroup>\n    <!-- Treat binding failures as build errors -->\n    <MauiStrictXamlCompilation>true</MauiStrictXamlCompilation>\n</PropertyGroup>\n```\n\nWith `x:DataType` set, the XAML compiler resolves bindings at compile time. A typo like `{Binding Themee}` will produce a **build error** instead of silently failing at runtime.\n\n### 3. Opting out for specific bindings\n\nIf a binding intentionally targets a different type (e.g., a parent element), disable compiled bindings locally:\n\n```xml\n<Label Text=\"{Binding Title, x:DataType=x:Null}\" />\n```\n\nThis reverts that single binding to the classic runtime-resolved mode.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"fe076d24-183f-4722-8077-21cdc585f71b","outputTokens":520},"id":"7d172270-be01-4381-b267-c164b61a3009","timestamp":"2026-04-04T00:59:12.151Z","parentId":"b024ed82-df8a-4640-8431-6a861aaf253f"}
